  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/31ebded3fca9e57fddb97b693c5888ff.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as John, a career criminal with a reprehensible past. Upon waking in an unknown hotel, bloodied, injured and having no memory of the last eight years, he struggles with his own thoughts. Tormented by nightmares and chronic pain, John must seek clarity amidst the madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.poster.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.webm?t=1773086594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.mp4?t=1773086594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed for the casual gamer. A psychological thriller with dialogue choices. No puzzles. No side-quests. Simple combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/684b9f9a1b86a5dc6e610fa2498f8f7b.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episodic:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: All 6 Episodes are playable with the base game! Episodes 2-6 have upgraded character models and character textures.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/31ebded3fca9e57fddb97b693c5888ff.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as John, a career criminal with a reprehensible past. Upon waking in an unknown hotel, bloodied, injured and having no memory of the last eight years, he struggles with his own thoughts. Tormented by nightmares and chronic pain, John must seek clarity amidst the madness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.poster.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.webm?t=1773086594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/6fc81c676093108bc211c268042bef5e.mp4?t=1773086594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed for the casual gamer. A psychological thriller with dialogue choices. No puzzles. No side-quests. Simple combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847160/extras/684b9f9a1b86a5dc6e610fa2498f8f7b.avif?t=1773086594\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episodic:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: All 6 Episodes are playable with the base game! Episodes 2-6 have upgraded character models and character textures.</p>",
